      Will Spider-Man: No Way Home be on Disney Plus?
      No Way Home is the only MCU movie not currently streaming on Disney+ due to the complicated rights situation surrounding Marvel's wall-crawler. As most will know, Sony holds the right to produce and distribute Spider-Man movies, which puts Marvel Studios and Disney+ in a rather tough spot.
